<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>Email Verification</title>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: "Roboto", Arial, sans-serif;
                background-color: #f5f5f7;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                color: #202124;
            }

            .container {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 600px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                background-color: #ffffff;
                padding: 24px;
                border-radius: 8px;
                box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                font-size: 16px;
                box-sizing: border-box;
            }

            h1 {
                color: #4285f4;
                font-size: 28px;
                text-align: center;
                margin-bottom: 24px;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 16px;
                color: #5f6368;
                line-height: 1.6;
                margin: 0 0 16px;
                text-align: left;
            }

            .code {
                display: block;
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 240px;
                margin: 24px auto;
                font-size: 36px;
                background-color: #f1f3f4;
                color: #1a73e8;
                text-align: center;
                padding: 16px;
                text-decoration: none;
                border-radius: 4px;
                font-weight: bold;
                letter-spacing: 1px;
                word-wrap: break-word;
            }

            .footer {
                font-size: 14px;
                color: #777;
                text-align: center;
                margin-top: 40px;
            }

            a {
                color: #4285f4;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            .footer p {
                margin: 5px 0;
            }
            @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
                .container {
                    padding: 16px;
                }
                h1 {
                    font-size: 24px;
                }
                .code {
                    max-width: 100%;
                    font-size: 32px;
                    padding: 12px;
                }
                p {
                    font-size: 14px;
                }
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Email Verification</h1>
            <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>
                We received a request to Reset Your
                <a href="">NexChat</a> Account Password to verify you enter this
                code.
            </p>

            <p class="code"><%= verificationCode %></p>

            <p>
                If you did not request this
                <a href="mailto:asif.emailservice@gmail.com"
                    >contact our support team</a
                > that code valid for 1 hour
                .
            </p>

            <div class="footer">
                <p>Best regards,<br />The Team</p>
                <p>
                    If you have any questions, feel free to
                    <a href="mailto:asif.emailservice@gmail.com">Ask</a>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
